      "side": 1,
      "message": "IMHO 100LOC to mock a single function is a bit overkill\nwouldn\u0027t be simpler to pass func(c context.Context, newRevision, oldRevision string) as a parameter to the function that need commit history? Test would pass a mock func and prod would pass a real func. If there is too much propagation to do, the parameter could be a field",
